Genome-ka RNA-ga fayraska waxaa lagu sii daayaa cytoplasm-ka; ka dib markii uu soo laabto genome-ka fayraska, genomic RNA oo ay weheliso glycoproteins-ka la isku duubay iyo borotiinnada nucleocapsid waxay sameeyaan xashiishadyo ay ku jiraan virions, kuwaas oo ku xidhan xuubka plasma-ka oo sii daaya fayraska.
