Guud ahaan, ka dib markii fayras uu soo galo martida, waxaa marka hore aqoonsan nidaamka difaaca jirka ee martida iyada oo loo marayo qaababka loo yaqaan 'pattern recognition receptors' (PRRs), oo ay ku jiraan noocyada C ee lectin, Toll receptor (TLR), NOD receptor (NLR) iyo RIG-I receptor (RLR).
Wadooyin kala duwan ayuu fayraska ku keenaa muujinta waxyeelada, bislaanshaha unugyada dendritic iyo sameynta interferons nooca I (IFNs), kuwaas oo xaddidaya faafitaanka fayraska isla markaana dardargelinaya fahagosis macrophage ee antigen-ka fayraska.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, borotiinka N ee SARS-CoV wuxuu ka caawin karaa fayraska inuu ka baxsado jawaabaha difaaca jirka.
Waqti yar kadib, jawaabta difaaca jirka ee la qabsiga ah ayaa ku biiray dagaalka fayraska.
T-ka, oo ay ku jiraan unugyada CD4+ iyo CD8+ waxay door muhiim ah ka ciyaaraan difaaca.
Unugyada CD4+ T waxay kiciyaan unugyada B inay soo saaraan unugyada difaaca ee ku takhasusay fayraska, unugyada CD8+ T waxay si toos ah u dilaan unugyada uu fayraska ku dhacay.
