Sida ku cad daabacaadda toddobaad (3 Maarso 2020), si loo xaqiijiyo kiiska la tuhunsan yahay, waxaa loo baahan yahay in la isku daro hal shay oo ka mid ah sheekada cudurka iyo laba shay oo ka mid ah dhacdooyinka bukaanka si loo sameeyo falanqayn dhammaystiran, ama saddex shay oo ka mid ah dhacdooyinka bukaanka waa in la buuxiyaa haddii aysan jirin taariikhda cudurka oo cad:
Taariikhda cudurka: (1) taariikhda safarka ama joogitaanka magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku dhow ama bulshooyinka kale ee kiisaska COVID-19 lagu soo warramey 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha bilaabashada; (2) taariikhda xiriir la leh kiisaska SARS-CoV-2 ee faafa (oo leh baaritaanka nucleic acid-ka ee togan); (3) taariikhda xiriir la leh bukaanka qaba qandho ama calaamadaha neefsashada ee ka yimid magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku dhow ama bulshooyinka kale ee kiisaska COVID-19 lagu soo warramey 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor calaamadaha bilaabashada; (4) taariikhda xiriir la leh kooxda kiisaska la xaqiijiyay (in ka badan ama u dhiganta laba kiis oo qandho iyo/ama calaamadaha neefsashada ah oo ka dhacay 2 toddobaad gudahood meelo yaryar sida guriga, xafiiska, fasalka iwm.).
Muuqaalada caafimaad: (1) qandho iyo/ama calaamadaha neefsashada; (2) oo leh muuqaal lagu ogaado cudurka COVID-19; (3) tirada guud ee unugyada dhiigga cad ee muujinaya tirada caadiga ah, hoos u dhac ama hoos u dhac ku yimid tirada unugyada lymphocyte ee marxaladda bilowga ah ee calaamadaha.
Cudurka la xaqiijiyay waa in lagu ogaadaa haddii uu yahay qof laga shakisan yahay mid ka mid ah waxyaabaha soo socda ee cudurka ama cudurka: (1) baaritaanka PCR ee wanaagsan ee SARS-CoV-2; (2) taxanaha fayraska oo dhan oo muujinaya isku midnimo sare oo la xiriirta coronavirus-yada cusub ee la yaqaan; (3) baaritaanka serum ee laga helay antibodies-ka IgM iyo IgG ee SARS-CoV-2; ama isbeddel ka yimid antibodies-ka IgG ee SARS-CoV-2 oo ka yimid mid xun oo noqday mid wanaagsan ama koror ka badan ama ka siman afar jeer heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka heerka.
