Sabtidii, war-saxaafadeed fiidiyoow ah oo lagu soo bandhigay internetka, Wasiirka Gaadiidka Wadooyinka iyo Buundooyinka ee Bengal Obaidul Quader ayaa sheegay in gaadiidka dadweynaha uu hakad geli doono waqti ka badan intii hore loo qorsheeyay, ilaa Sabtida soo socota.
