Qorshe lagu xaddidayo safarka u dhexeeya magaalooyinka ayaa la shaaciyay bishii Maarso, inkasta oo gaadiidka culus ee u dhexeeya magaalooyinka ka hor sanadka cusub ee Farshaxa ee Nowruz uu sii socday.
