Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-converting enzyme type 2' (ECA2) waa enzyme ku xidhan dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ECA2 waxay joojineysaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-converting enzyme' (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa tirada angiotensin II iyo kor u qaadida Ang (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. ECA2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa inay tahay barta laga galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada.
Nooca bini aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hECA2.
Nooca 2 ee angiotensin-converting enzyme waa metaloenzyme zinc ku jira oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada iyo unugyada kale.
Baraha ECA2 wuxuu leeyahay domain N-terminal M2 peptidase iyo domain C-terminal oo ah amino acids iyo colectin-ka wadayaasha nidaamka kelyaha.
ECA2 waa borotiinka noocka 1 ee unugyada, oo leh heerka firfircoon ee loo yaqaan 'enzymatically active domain' oo ku yaal dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Dhinaca kale, ECA2 waxaa laga kala saaraa dhinaca transmembrane-ka ee enzymes kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, waxaana soo baxa borotiinka lagu milmi karo ee loo yaqaan 'sheddase' oo lagu sii daayo dhiigga, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu saaraa kaadida.
ECA2 waxay ku jirtaa xubno badan: ECA2 waxay ku xirantahay xuubka unugyada unugyada waaweyn ee nooca II ee sanbabada, unugyada qanjirka mindhicirka, unugyada dhiigga iyo xididdada iyo unugyada muruqyada sanbabada ee unugyada badankood.
ECA2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, jirka, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
